  "texts": [
    "Thus, observed lenses are manifestly non-circular.",
    "Generalising a circular lens to an elliptical one is easy, one only has to add a term",
    "to the lens potential ψ of a circular lens.",
    "The additional term is called external shear (or XS).",
    "By construction, external shear is traceless and hence implies no change in κ, that is, in the mass distribution."
  ],
